title: Once a G.O.P. Stalwart, Liz Cheney Hits the Trail for Democrats
description: Stumping for Elissa Slotkin in Michigan, Ms. Cheney had an urgent message for voters: “We all must stand and defend the republic.”
dc:creator: Jonathan Weisman
media:credit: Emily Elconin for The New York Times
media:description: Representative Liz Cheney campaigning for Elissa Slotkin, a House colleague, on Tuesday in East Lansing, Mich. She said it was the first time she had campaigned for a Democrat.
